Model Number: A1642 Anker 334 MagGo Battery (PowerCore 10K) The Snap and Go Magnetic Power Bank Huge Capacity, Slim Design: Experience massive 10,000mAh power in the slim and lightweight power bank—perfect for on-the-go charging. Consistent Power, Enduring Quality: Anker 334 MagGo Battery maintains 90% battery even after 20 months, exceeding industry standards. Colorful and Snappy: Embrace vividness through Anker 334 MagGo Battery's colorful design—creating a strong and secure attachment to iPhone 12, 13, 14 series, and beyond. Case-Friendly MagSafe Power: Tailored for compatibility with MagSafe cases, offering iPhone charging convenience without the need to remove the case. Please note that it is not suitable for non-MagSafe phone cases. Compatibility: iPhone 15, iPhone 15 Pro, iPhone 15 Plus, iPhone 15 Pro Max, iPhone 14, iPhone 14 Pro, iPhone 14 Plus, iPhone 14 Pro Max, iPhone 13, iPhone 13 Pro, iPhone 13 Pro Max, iPhone 13 mini, iPhone 12, iPhone 12 Pro, iPhone 12 Pro Max, and iPhone 12 mini. Notes: The magnetic charging offers a maximum power of up to 7.5W. Use only with magnetic phone cases. Not compatible with non-magnetic phone cases, such as OtterBox Defender cases.

Why is my power bank providing fewer charges than expected? The capacity reduction during charging is due to a 30% to 45% energy loss in the battery cells and conversion circuitry. Therefore, a fully charged Anker 334 MagGo Battery (PowerCore 10K) offers an estimated 5,500mAh to 7,000mAh to power devices. How can I estimate the number of charges for my device? To estimate charging cycles, use these formula: (Power Bank Capacity × 0.55) ÷ Device Battery Capacity ≈ Number of Charges. For instance, charging a 3,000mAh device using a 10,000mAh power bank would offer approximately 2.16 charges.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice Wireless Charger
reviews.reviewText: The battery works well to charge the iPhone 15 pro max. The magsafe properties perform well to keep the battery attached to the phone. It is a little bulkier than I expected, which is more about my unrealistic expectations than the battery's actual size. It adds quite a bit of weight to the phone, so don't expect to want to carry it around attached to the phone. The case is somewhat slippery, and would benefit from surface textured grips on the sides to make it easier to hold onto when on the phone in use and when attaching and removing the battery. I'm not quite getting the battery life I expected. I'm getting about 1-1/2 charges between recharging. The magsafe battery does work to charge my phone when the charging cable is plugged in; however, the USB-A port does not operate when the charging cable is plugged in to the USB-C port. Not a big issue since I can plug a USB-C cable into the iPhone and use it as a charger while the battery recharges the iPhone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It does what it promises
reviews.reviewText: I used it to charge my iPhone 14 Pro Max, it charges quick, however from 40 percent to 100 it did use about half of the stored battery power. I do imagine that the fact that it is an iPhone Pro Max has much to do with the Anker draining faster.Pro: Has great magnetic connectivty with the iPhone and magsafe, and has a USB-A port to charge devices that are not magasafe.I am happy with my purchase, I got it for around $34 Feb 2024

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It is an anker product what more do I need to say. From my first anker product I’ve ever purchased I noticed right away the quality, durability, functionality, styling, and longevity of the product and this one is no different. It has a great matte finish with glossy letters that subtly say anker. I have the purple iPhone and this one is a purple tint that matches perfectly, the product snaps right to the back stays on fairly well, it’s not meant to be swung around while on but you can certainly use the phone or go about your business with light being tethered to a wall. I use this thing on many other products, mostly plugged in. Not every product can accept the charge by placing the unit on it so you can just plug right into it. When I expect to be out all day on business or riding my motorcycle this thing always comes with me. It’s a battery, it has some weight to it but you’re also free to move around. Highly recommend

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Anker Magnetic Power Bank 10,000mAh Review: Unrivaled Charging Convenience if it works
reviews.reviewText: As a tech enthusiast constantly on the move, I recently added the Anker Magnetic Power Bank 10,000mAh to my arsenal of charging accessories, and it has quickly become a game-changer for my daily routine.**Magnetic Attachment:**The standout feature of this power bank is its magnetic design, which seamlessly attaches to the back of my smartphone, providing a secure and hassle-free charging experience. The magnetic connection is strong, and it aligns effortlessly with my device, ensuring a stable connection without the need for fumbling with cables or precise positioning.**Impressive 20W Fast Charging:**With a 20W fast charging capability, this power bank delivers a quick and efficient charge to my devices. Whether it's my smartphone, wireless earbuds, or other compatible gadgets, the Anker Magnetic Power Bank ensures that I spend less time waiting for my devices to recharge and more time using them.**Wireless Charging Convenience:**The wireless charging feature is a game-changer, allowing me to charge my Qi-compatible devices without the need for cables. The convenience of simply placing my device on the power bank and having it charge wirelessly is a significant plus, especially when I'm on the go and want to minimize the number of cables I need to carry.**Compact and Portable Design:**The compact and lightweight design of this power bank makes it easy to slip into my pocket or bag, making it an ideal companion for travel or daily commutes. Despite its small size, the 10,000mAh capacity provides enough power to keep my devices charged throughout the day, and the matte finish adds a touch of sophistication.**Multi-Device Compatibility:**The Anker Magnetic Power Bank is not limited to smartphones; it supports a variety of devices, including wireless earbuds, smartwatches, and more. The versatility of this power bank makes it a go-to solution for charging all my essential gadgets with ease.**Build Quality and Durability:**Anker is known for producing high-quality products, and this power bank is no exception. The build quality is top-notch, and it feels robust and durable. The materials used inspire confidence in its ability to withstand the rigors of daily use.**LED Indicator and User-Friendly Design:**The LED indicator on the power bank provides a quick and easy way to check the remaining battery level. The user-friendly design ensures that even those unfamiliar with technology can use this power bank effortlessly.In conclusion, the Anker Magnetic Power Bank 10,000mAh is a stellar combination of convenience, speed, and versatility. Its magnetic attachment feature, fast charging capabilities, and compact design make it an indispensable accessory for anyone in need of reliable on-the-go power. Anker has once again delivered a product that stands out in a crowded market. Highly recommended!******EDIT******So I've had this about three months and it was working great, until it wasn't. Now it won't charge, doesn't light up, nothing works. I have a $50 paperweight now.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My daughter burns through her batter so fast!!!! This is amazing to carry with us, I love the wireless technology so we don’t have to carry all the cords. We get a good 3-4 charges from this. It’s a little heavy, but well worth the price.
This thing is so compact and cute, also charges fast. The magnets are strong. I recommend it.

Die Anker 334 MagGo Powerbank ist einfach unglaublich! Mit einer enormen Kapazität von 10.000mAh bietet sie erstaunliche 22 Stunden zusätzliche Videowiedergabezeit auf dem iPhone 14. Das kabellose Laden mit 7,5W und einer magnetischen Kraft von 10N ist beeindruckend und funktioniert sogar besser als das originale MagSafe-Ladegerät.Die Powerbank ist außerdem schlank und mobil, mit kompakten Abmessungen von 10,67 cm × 6,86 cm × 1,83 cm, passt sie mühelos in jede Tasche oder den Rucksack.Ein weiterer großer Vorteil ist die Möglichkeit, dein iPhone aufzuladen und gleichzeitig die Anker 334 Magnetische Powerbank aufzuladen. Kein langes Warten auf volle Leistung mehr!Im Lieferumfang enthalten sind die Anker 334 MagGo Powerbank (PowerCore 10K), ein 60cm langes USB-A auf USB-C Kabel, eine Bedienungsanleitung, 18 Monate Herstellergarantie und freundlicher Kundenservice.Alles in allem kann ich die Anker 334 MagGo Powerbank wärmstens empfehlen. Sie ist leistungsstark, praktisch und bietet eine großartige Lösung für unterwegs, um sicherzustellen, dass dein iPhone stets aufgeladen ist.
Un produit au top du top sur tout pour les utilisateurs iPhone je le recommande 1000foix
